# Kalibr SDK

**Multi-Model AI Integration Framework**

Write once. Deploy anywhere. Connect to any AI model.

Kalibr lets developers expose any Python function as a model-compatible API â€” instantly usable by GPT, Claude, Gemini, and beyond.

